{"tid":1623824,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《蘋果》懸紅50萬 追緝襲擊女記者兇徒","createTime":"2019-10-05T01:50:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T01:51:51.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c398b2e630888c6c3da8f84e1cee83a6f71c08f9","tid":1623824,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:50:43.000Z","msg":"《蘋果日報》女記者9.24遭4名兇徒襲擊，全城憤怒，《蘋果》發出嚴正聲明，強烈譴責兇徒暴行，並懸紅50萬元，發動全城緝兇，希望市民提供消息，協助將兇徒繩之於法。<br />\n<br />\n全文如下︰<br />\n<br />\n2019年9月24日（星期二）晚上約8時15分，《蘋果日報》一名女記者在秀茂坪順天邨天權樓地下大快活，遭4名穿黑衣黑褲的蒙面男子襲擊，部份行兇者當時頭戴黃色頭盔。<br />\n<br />\n本報現懸紅港幣50萬元正。任何公眾人士若有此案的消息、或知悉兇徒的身份或下落，請盡速聯絡本報。凡在案發起半年內，提供資料致使兇徒繩之於法者（即被檢控並在本港法院就此案作出答辯），將可全數或按比例分配賞格。<br />\n<br />\n聯絡本報可致電24小時報料熱線2929 0000 、手機短訊6383 6568或電郵adnews@appledaily.com<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mrPp5x9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmrPp5x9.jpg&h=294bea7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191006/60083332\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191006%2F60083332&d=Bs0XXOgOekCAei%2FiISrrFhZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=46257a1d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191006%2F60083332&h=6748ce7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191006/60083332</a>"},{"pid":"33351b1d5c1b289762bb507138ff1e0e4149bb32","tid":1623824,"uid":125553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:51:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cd5QgFd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcd5QgFd.jpg&h=94e026d7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wn01oke.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWn01oke.png&h=05ec47f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3VGv06V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3VGv06V.jpg&h=df9b3af5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}